@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect and use your information when you register for events through our platform.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>When you sign up for an event, we collect your name and email address. This information is used solely for event management purposes and to send you updates about the events you've registered for.</p>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Confirm your registration for events</li>
    <li>Send event reminders and updates</li>
    <li>Manage attendee lists for event organizers</li>
</ul>

<h3>Information Sharing</h3>
<p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties. Your contact details are only visible to event organizers for the specific events you register for.</p>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at privacy@eventsignup.com.</p>

<p><small>Last updated: February 2026</small></p>
